{"tid":2395521,"cid":15,"subCid":0,"title":"【 ﻿走資去台灣﻿ 】Citibank 全球速匯申請及操作分享","createTime":"2021-02-05T03:01:12.000Z","updateTime":"2021-02-12T15:28:53.000Z","uid":237115,"like":5,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":9,"replies":[{"pid":"ec6dcb2d1c93e072c8e41c7f370d05bc3aff5cdb","tid":2395521,"uid":237115,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-05T03:01:12.000Z","msg":"#0手續費  #開戶操作教學  #移民歐美一樣ok<br />\n<br />\n當你人到咗台灣，需要從香港匯較大筆款項（例如十萬港元以上），抑或想將手上美金匯到台灣 (或其他地區)，甚至乎入金美國券商 (e.g. Firstrade) 作投資，有經營 YouTube、網購等需要美元往來，Citibank 全球速匯係慳手續費嘅好幫手。<br />\n<br />\n如果你是香港花旗的用戶，可以到台灣花旗開戶 (要預約，帶居留證/身分證/護照/印章/香港花旗帳戶資料)，向職員表示要辦理活期儲蓄+全球速匯服務，然後就係一連串流程，免費申請。<br />\n<br />\n聽說匯豐、部分台資銀行都有類似服務，我冇用過，唔清楚詳情，希望有巴絲可以分享多啲 info。<br />\n<br />\n花旗 Citibank 全球速匯有個位要小心操作，一做錯，匯率極差。<br />\n繼續睇：<br />\nMeWe: <a href=\"http://bit.ly/3rAYcin\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fbit.ly%2F3rAYcin&d=GtJgxCFvwMhqeg%2B2Fxb9ERD7%2Fo0bOSfVmdYqJtNqH20%3D&h=469bb6c1\" target=\"_blank\">http://bit.ly/3rAYcin</a><br />\nIG: <a href=\"https://bit.ly/3aAUVIL\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fbit.ly%2F3aAUVIL&d=GtJgxCFvwMhqeg%2B2Fxb9ERD7%2Fo0bOSfVmdYqJtNqH20%3D&h=a76fc8e8\" target=\"_blank\">https://bit.ly/3aAUVIL</a>"},{"pid":"a33d62bdf50f7927e78ef7674959d6602b2cc910","tid":2395521,"uid":319687,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2021-02-05T03:26:09.000Z","msg":"Citi 台灣 只比香港人開Citi Priority 以上的<br />\n普通Citi account 唔比開<br />\n冇80萬台幣入金就冇得諗"},{"pid":"c47fa012f1b02cfc19f13bf27d97775ea4f31b7a","tid":2395521,"uid":74361,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-02-05T04:16:07.000Z","msg":"可唔可以張D錢匯返香港?"},{"pid":"e79fc98217732fe91be647cf0935178cf8f0023f","tid":2395521,"uid":237115,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"c47fa012f1b02cfc19f13bf27d97775ea4f31b7a","tid":2395521,"uid":74361,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-02-05T04:16:07.000Z","msg":"可唔可以張D錢匯返香港?"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-05T10